messages.text: Dude check it out
Wassup
Rachael from class is totally diggin on me
WHAT NO WAY
Yeah it was weird. She texted me out of nowhere
Said she got my number from someone else
Ooooo so she’s comin after you eh?
Check it. I been textin her like crazy
My man. What you guys been talkin about?
Just basic stuff. She’s really cool
Bro ask her out
What?! Dude it’s too soon!
Go big or go home boy
You’re just trying to mess this up for me!
Like you messed up all my other relationships!
Dude those chicks were crazy. I was doing you a favor.
Whatever man. Just stay out of this one, alright?
Haha whatever you say man
Dude she asked me out!!!
Wait what?
Yeah! Out of nowhere!
ooohhh man this is going so well
I’m terrified. That means I got some bad luck coming my way
Nah dude it just means your a good guy.
And someone is finally seeing that
Wow, thanks Luke.
No problem
So when you guys going out?
Good question! Hold up I’ll ask her.
DUDE! SHE WANTS TO GO OUT TONIGHT
Okay good stop yelling
Haha sorry yo
Man this is exciting. You know what you gonna wear?
Crap…I didn’t even think of that!
This is why you have me, the Luke.
What? Nobody calls you “The Luke"
You just did. Anyway, hurry up and go get ready! You only have an hour
You’re right okay I’m going.
What do you think about the red sweater vest I’ve been saving?
Oh, so then you don’t plan on ever losing your virginity
You’re right, bad move with the sweater vest
Just go with the flannel and the beanie
Be yourself
Okay. Okay. okay. You’re right. Just play it cool
Exactly! Also, make sure you bring a bottle of water with you.
Water? Why?
For good measure. You’re gonna be totally nervous and your throat will get dry
Fair enough
Alright, I’m on the way to the bus stop.
Bus stop? duuuuude
I’m NOT taking my dad’s car. He’ll kill me!
Bro, but isn’t it worth?
Crap
What?
She wants to get ice cream after the movie!
So?
Movie ends at 10
The buses don’t run that late!
See what I mean?
You may not get this chance again
MMmmmmmm I’m scared yo
Think of it this way
If your dad finds out, at least you’ll have a good story
Actually, I’m not sure if he’s gonna believe you went out with a girl...
Dude you aren’t helping!
Haha I’m kidding I’m kidding.
But seriously, take the car.
My dad is SO going to kill me...
I did it! I took the car!
Man this is such a rush! I feel great!
Don’t lose focus, John. You still have a date to not screw up
Shut up man I got this
Let me know when you get there.
I’ll try and keep giving you advice
I don’t need your advice!
If you say so, sweater boy
Ugh okay I’ll keep you updated.
okay I’m at her place, but this place looks weird
Weird? What do you mean weird?
Well it’s really dark and this is the only house inn the area
Just doesn’t look like anybody is here
try going around the back?
Maybe it’s one of those houses
I guess I’ll give it a shot
Ugh it’s so dark back here
What? No lights in the house are on?
That’s the thing
There aren’t even any windows. Just the front door.
I’m gonna go back around to the front and wait.
She told me to just go inside and sit down.
She’s getting ready.
Yeah just go wait for her.
The door is already cracked open...
She probably knew you were close and left it open for you
I wouldn’t worry about it
Okay I’m inside. Took me forever to find a light
You made the right choice man. You can’t pass this up
Luke I don’t know how I feel about this
There’s nothing in this house but a table and some plywood.
There aren’t even any bedrooms! I’m getting the hell out of here.
Whoa you’re gonna leave?
The door just shut behind me. It won’t open up!!
Dude just chill out. She said she’d be ready soon right?
Yeah...she did...
So just wait for her man.
Wait.
You knew
What? I knew what?
back when I was getting ready
You knew I only had an hour to get ready
But all I told you was that she wanted to go out tonight.
Lucky guess?
Luke what the hell is going on
LUKE WHAT IS THIS
It’s a shame John, really
You thought you had a chance with someone like Rachael
What?! LET ME OUT OF THIS HOUSE NOW LUKE
Someone so…selfish
So… naive
Luke I don’t know what you’re talking about
But this is insane Luke we can talk about this
Whatever is going on we can work this out!
LUKE!
There’s nothing else to work out, John
LUKE THE ROOM JUST LIT ON FIRE
Luke this isn’t funny anymore this place is burning down!!!
Well then. I hope you brought along that water.
